  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Cesarean section is a surgical procedure used to deliver one or more babies. cesarean section
      is usually performed when vaginal delivery will put the mother or child's health or life at
      risk. In recent years, the number of cesarean section has risen worldwide.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
